name: Kendoll Janner
description: What is the project about? KEN is a decentralized fair launch token with the total supply in circulation. 100% of the supply was added to the liquidity pool, and the LP was burned at launch. The contract has been renounced which means KEN belongs to the community. What makes your project unique? We are building interesting experiences and tech with the help of AI. Using video storytelling to build an interactive web3 world which KEN will be used in. History of your project: We are a new project and just launched about a week ago, but the community members building around the token have been active builders in web3 for a very long time.
